HEADWORD: anteflexion
<hw>an`te*flex"ion</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧n`t⟦esl⟧*fl⟦ecr⟧k"sh⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A displacement forward of an organ,
